====User icons====
[[File:VRChat Plus Icons.webp|thumb|200x200px|User Icons can be displayed on a user's nameplate if they are subscribed to VRC+.]]
[[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory#User Icons|User Icons]] are circular images that can be equipped for both profiles and groups. When equipped to your profile, the icon is displayed on your nameplate, in the Here tab, at the top of the Quick Menu, and on your profile, replacing the free icon of the first 3 characters of your username.